title: Tropical Spa by Creativity For Kids
description: Don't girls of all ages love spa days? You tropical spa day begins with an inflatable flamingo pedicure pool, water bead spa mask, a pineapple nail file, foam toe separators, 130+ pieces of gold.

title: Mini Color Pencil By Number Kits
description: Introduce young artists to colored pencil drawing with a Mini Color Pencil By Number Kit. Each kit includes ten colored pencils, one 5 in. x 7 in. pre-printed design board, and a numbered overlay.

title: Enchanted Fairy Garden by Creativity For Kids
description: Create and grow a magical miniature fairy land. With a little creative magic, you can grow an enchanted fairy world. This garden set includes an 11 in. flower shaped garden dish and an enchanted flower house.
